            <p>Yours of 16th with $250 (for my lecture<ptr target="yal.00238_n3"/> of Thursday night afternoon preceding) safely
                rec'd&#8212;&amp; this is the receipt. Thanks&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
            <postscript>
                <p> will write you again in a day or two </p>
